    <briefdescription>
<para>Firmware update state machine class implemented according to C++ state machine design pattern. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The class provides the four states Idle, Triggered, Firmware download and Ready and handler functions for the events OtaStart, FwInfo, DlComplete, DlFailed and timer expired. <image type="html" name="FwFsm.png" inline="yes"></image>
 </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
